snippet.title: After1.5 years, Psycho Bathroom is releasing on April 29th!
snippet.description:
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1601340/Psycho_Bathroom/

An Action Game Where You’re A Toothbrush Fighting Toilet Plumes

Psycho Bathroom is a 2D boss-fight game. In the bathroom you reside in, your toilet lid is broken. Every toilet flush is splashing aerosols all over the place. You, as a toothbrush, must eradicate the threat and protect your master.

Upgrade your gear! Meet new buddies! Bond with your master and explore his dark but comic story.
